  Milano stars as Charlotte Wells, a sensuous but innocent virginal college freshman. She is being seduced by an obsessive lover which only comes to her in her dreams. The lover is a vampire, played by Martin Kemp. He has been waging his own battle for survival, and his time is about to run out. He has only three days to find a virgin and draw the lifeblood from her in order to survive. Otherwise, he will cease to exist.
